These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-1::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bluemaster, oliveros, swisher, vegafina
1. the oliveros-smoker is in an odd position##4
2. the vegafina-smoker is between the bluemaster-smoker and the oliveros-smoker##2
3. the vegafina-smoker is on the right of the bluemaster-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| Cigar   | bluemaster | vegafina | oliveros | swisher |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-2::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: september, may, november, june
1. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1
2. the person who's birthday is in may is in an odd position##4
3. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in september##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |    2    |   3    |   4   |
| Birthday   | may | september | june | november |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-3::.
4 different games are played: backgammon, bridge, canasta, mah-jongg
1. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left or right of the person playing backgammon##3
2. the person playing backgammon is in an odd position##4
3. the person playing canasta is between the person playing mah-jongg and the person playing bridge##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2    |    3    |      4       |
| Game   | backgammon | mah-jongg | canasta | bridge |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-4::.
City: venice, london, san-francisco, boston
1. the person traveling to london is on the left or right of the person traveling to venice##3
2. the person traveling to san-francisco is in an even position##4
3. the person traveling to boston is between the person traveling to venice and the person traveling to san-francisco##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |    2     |       3       |   4    |
| City   | london | venice | boston | san-francisco |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-5::.
4 different pets are kept: ferret, rabbit, lizard, bird
1. the owner of the ferret is in an even position##4
2. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1
3. the owner of the rabbit is on the left or right of the owner of the lizard##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |    2     |    3    |    4     |
| Pet   | bird | ferret | lizard | rabbit |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-6::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, lacrosse, climbing, skiing
1. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the far right##1
2. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left or right of the person who's sport is skiing##3
3. the person who's sport is climbing is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |  3   |    4    |
| Sport   | climbing | cycling | skiing | lacrosse |

