2. the owner of the turtle is between the owner of the guinea-pig and the owner of the cat##2
3. the owner of the guinea-pig is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2     |      3      |   4    |
| Pet   | rat | cat | turtle | guinea-pig |

