.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-14::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: skydiving, sudoku, hiking, rock-climbing
1. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
2. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##3
3. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##3
4. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |       2       |    3     |   4   |
| Hobby   | hiking | rock-climbing | skydiving | sudoku |

