.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-17::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: purple, pink, light-blue, red
1. the person who likes purple is on the left of the person who likes red##1
2. the person who likes red is on the left of the person who likes light-blue##1
3. the person who likes red is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |   2   |  3   |     4     |
| Color   | purple | red | light-blue | pink |

