.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-18::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: subway, trike, bike, boat
1. the person driving the bike is in an odd position##4
2. the person driving the trike is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person driving the bike is between the person driving the trike and the person driving the subway##2

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1     |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Transport   | boat | subway | bike | trike |

