.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-19::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: davidoff, swisher, siglo, cain
1. the swisher-smoker is the swisher-smoker##1
2. the cain-smoker is on the left or right of the siglo-smoker##3
3. the siglo-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
4. the davidoff-smoker is in an even position##4
5. the cain-smoker is on the left of the swisher-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2      |   3   |    4    |
| Cigar   | siglo | cain | swisher | davidoff |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-20::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: van, boat, quad-bike, bike
1. the person driving the quad-bike is in an odd position##4
2. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1
3. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left or right of the person driving the boat##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1    |         2          |    3    |    4     |
| Transport   | van | bike | quad-bike | boat |

 